rows.name: Here we are! Yanchik Harbor, isn't it?

rows.label: fev11_140_175_msg0002

That's correct. I requested that they
wait specially for Laura-sama before
they depart

rows.label: fev11_140_175_msg0003

Looks like getting our ride to Gula
will be no trouble at all.

rows.label: fev11_140_175_msg0005

Come on, let's go and have a chat
with the captain.
